annotations:
  artifacthub.io/changes: |
    - kind: changed
      description: "Per-component env: entries may now be a map instead of a scalar. A scalar is rendered as the variable's value:; a map is passed through verbatim as its valueFrom:, so a custom env var can be sourced from a Secret (secretKeyRef), ConfigMap (configMapKeyRef), or the pod's own metadata (fieldRef) instead of being inlined. Scalar values behave exactly as before. See docs/CUSTOMIZATIONS.md."
